# Cloud Build upload context — keep it to what Dockerfile.train COPYs
# (pyproject.toml, uv.lock, src/, main.py, infra/gcp/entrypoint.sh).
# Patterns are ANCHORED with a leading slash: an unanchored `data/` would also
# exclude src/mini_networks/core/data/ (it did — broken image, 2026-07-10).
/.git
/.venv
/node_modules
/playground/node_modules
/playground/out
/playground/.next
/runs/
/data/
/legacy/
/mlruns/
/infra/gcp/terraform/.terraform/
__pycache__/
*.pt
